title: Take Two

description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions

Edited by Diane Kang 

 

Kate loses the battle against Apple and buys a new computer. Leisha gets a new shirt with very specific instructions. And they both agree working out solo will always beat group workouts filled with nonstop chatter.
